{"tid":2262557,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"控方指鍾翰林洗黑錢近70萬 涉及於專頁上眾籌","createTime":"2020-10-29T08:03:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-29T19:09:09.000Z","uid":240362,"like":9,"dislike":202,"uniUserReply":90,"replies":[{"pid":"2dc4464ac1edd34d83c3fd3ae5f78e2dce0d2acf","tid":2262557,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T08:03:48.000Z","msg":"前學生動源召集人鍾翰林被落案起訴分裂國家罪、兩項處理已知道或相信為代表從可公訴罪行的得益的財產罪，以及一項串謀發佈煽動性刊物罪，案件今早於西九龍裁判法院提堂，案件押至明年1月7日再訊。據控方的案情指，鍾被控的兩項洗黑錢控罪，涉及他管理的專頁帖文附有由他開設的戶口連結，他從戶口先後接收多筆存款，款項由2元至3萬元不等，共涉近70萬，相信涉及眾籌，而資金流動與其學生背景完全不相符。<br />\n<br />\n控方又指，專頁帖文附有Paypal戶口連結募捐，Paypal戶口由鍾開設，連結到鍾的匯豐戶口。案情指Paypal戶口自2018年1月至今年7月接收共13.3萬元，來自109筆存款，絕大部分會轉至匯豐戶口，而匯豐戶口自去年9月起共接收56.4萬元。控方指，鍾報稱是職訓局全日制學生，上述款項流動完全不符合其收入和學生背景。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201029/NGCWYIMHQRHI5PZUOX4B2ANJ7Y/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201029%2FNGCWYIMHQRHI5PZUOX4B2ANJ7Y%2F&d=2u41qa%2Bce9Gslgrzp%2F5KiqNZBGycwMyv8OGD44uLuTw%3D&h=2c9e5fee\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201029%2FNGCWYIMHQRHI5PZUOX4B2ANJ7Y%2F&h=1006a258\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201029/NGCWYIMHQRHI5PZUOX4B2ANJ7Y/</a>"},{"pid":"7c9edcb9022c7150792a0a5954b7e4f3dd53ed4c","tid":2262557,"uid":135276,"like":58,"dislike":2,"score":56,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T08:06:20.000Z","msg":"D patreon KOL<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec546e218f310996f3dc436cee8ed9063746a2db","tid":2262557,"uid":12554,"like":41,"dislike":2,"score":39,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T08:13:00.000Z","msg":"目的係打擊其他眾籌風氣？"},{"pid":"adff1c83811c7a23ea31e0ea6f22f139486af064","tid":2262557,"uid":92340,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T08:14:00.000Z","msg":"咁捐嗰啲咪共犯？"},{"pid":"64a75a79c5e48b9a9d6b7a385699ed0e5f5c623f","tid":2262557,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy